3
) quite long, without setae (epm 
3
s). Antemetaspiracular setae (asp 
3
s) absent. Metathoracic spiracle (sp 
3
) 15–20 μm wide. Metasternum (stn 
3
) lightly sclerotised; metasternal setae (stn 
3
